  "description": "<p>Give into your powder jones without getting weighed down or thrown off balance. With smart organization and a balanced carry system, the Micon is light and tight so you stay stable whether skinning up or skiing down. Separated compartments, including a dedicated avi tool compartment and soft-lined lid compartment, provide easy access to your gear without having to dig through your whole pack.</p><ul><li>210-denier Cordura nylon with a 200-denier liquid crystal polymer grid for tear protection</li><li>Laminated fabric and taped critical seams keep out water</li><li>Lightly padded back panel with single aluminum stay transfer load to your hips</li><li>Laminated shoulder straps and a padded hipbelt provide a comfortable and supportive suspension system</li><li>RollTop\u2122 closure and WaterTight\u2122 urethane-coated side zipper are highly water-resistant</li><li>Full-length side zipper provides access to main compartment without dumping everything out</li><li>Avalanche tool pocket keeps your safety gear organized</li><li>Top pocket stores goggles, camera, or other delicate items</li><li>Gear loops and ice clipper slots keep gear close at hand</li><li>Attachments for poles, ice tools and helmet</li></ul>",
